Completed 2026-05-19 via FULL-rigor sub-agent (parallel C-Parallel-2 batch with tasks 044-048).

**Option A (DELETE) chosen** per POML preference. All /debug/* endpoints removed entirely; no #if DEBUG gating.

## Endpoints removed (11 total)

