From `Infrastructure/DI/EndpointMappingExtensions.cs` (3 narrow Edits):
9. GET /debug/token — JWT-claim-leaking endpoint (audit C-2 specific call-out)
- Also: removed `app.MapDebugEndpoints()` registration in `MapSpaarkeEndpoints`
- Also: updated `/status` endpoint — removed `version = "1.0.1-debug"` → `1.0.2`, removed `debugEndpoints` array from response payload
